= Check Sequence Files Status =
#context: sop

"""Visualize Sequence Files Status"""

== Overview ==
Use Houdini Point data to visualize sequence file size (range from min to max), and the modified time (from now).
[Image:opdef:.?check_seq_files.png]

TIP:
    There are some point attributes to show the file status, ex: *size*, *mod_time*, *frame*, *file_path*, *exists*
    non-exists file will show in red color and in *non_exist* point group
    Also, there are point groups: *size* and *time*.

@parameters
Files:
    #id: files
    Sequence files to visualize
    
Start/End:
    #id: frame_range
    Frame range
    
Preview Length:
    #id: preview_length
    Generated points range in X-axis
    
Preview Height:
    #id: preview_height
    Generated points range in Y-axis
    
Font Size:
    #id: font_size
    Size of guide font